A federal judge sentenced a North Carolina man to 14 years in prison for giving a Maryland woman silicone butt injections before her death, officials said.

Vinnie Lysander Taylor, 44, of Wilmington, North Carolina, traveled the country injecting women with silicone that he said would give them larger buttocks, and at least one of the women died days after undergoing the procedure at a hotel in Capitol Heights, Maryland, according to prosecutors.
